{"title":"Get one of the last HomePods ever for $44 off","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/340360/get-one-of-the-last-homepods-ever-for-44-off.html","date":1616531690000,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd\">\n<html><body><div id=\"link_wrapped_content\">\n<section class=\"wp-block-bigbite-multi-title\"><div class=\"container\"></div></section><p>The HomePod is <a href=\"https://www.macworld.co.uk/news/apple-kills-homepod-shift-focus-mini-3802669/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.macworld.co.uk/news/apple-kills-homepod-shift-focus-mini-3802669/\">about to become a collector&rsquo;s item</a>, so if you want one, you should act fast. And if you want to save on the $299 MSRP, you should act even faster. <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://eshop.macsales.com/item/Apple/MQHV2LLA/&amp;xcust=1-1-340360-0-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://eshop.macsales.com/item/Apple/MQHV2LLA/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OWC is selling the HomePod in white for $254.75</a>, good for $44 off and likely the best price you&rsquo;ll see before it&rsquo;s gone forever. The model OWC is selling is described as new, but comes in &ldquo;bulk&rdquo; packaging, meaning you won&rsquo;t get Apple&rsquo;s original box. You won&rsquo;t get an Apple warranty ever, but you will get a 1-year OWC Fulfilled Limited Warranty.&rdquo;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The HomePod released in 2018 to much fanfare and <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/3254179/apple-homepod-review.html\">high marks for its sound system</a>, but its $349 price tag was too much to bear in the face of cheaper competitors from Amazon, Google, and Sonos. Even after a price cut to $299, HomePod struggled to sell, but there&rsquo;s no denying its tremendous sound and room-shaking bass. It&rsquo;s a fantastic companion for an Apple Music or Apple One subscription and can play tunes from other services via AirPlay 2. Apple has promised to open up the platform to third-party services, but so far only Pandora has signed on.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>While the HomePod is being discontinued, Apple has promised to continue supporting it alongside the HomePod mini. And as we&rsquo;ve seen with previously retired Apple products, they tend to increase in value so if nothing else, a HomePod could a good investment. </p>\n\n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"wp-block-product-widget-block product-widget\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__block-title-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"product-widget__block-title\" id=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</h4>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__title-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"product-widget__title\" id=\"apple-homepod\">Apple HomePod</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__image-outer-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__image-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"product-widget__image\" src=\"https://images.idgesg.net/images/article/2018/01/homepod_space_gray_shelf-100747950-orig.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Apple HomePod\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"review product-widget__review-details\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__rating-and-review-link\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__review-details--rating\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"starRating\" style=\"--rating: 3;\" aria-label=\"Rating of this product is 3 out of 5\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><a class=\"product-widget__review-link\" href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/230983/apple-homepod-review.html\" target=\"_blank\">Read our review</a>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div classname=\"product-widget__information\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__